title: Videohive - After Effects Project Files - News Ident Pack
description:
News Ident Pack, is a new news package template with a lot of broadcast news elements and on air graphics. Contains: Opener, Headlines, lower thirds, Ots, Split Screens, Info Screens, Weather, Sport, business and Breaking News Openers and many more. This project offers you cool and easy way to customize a NEWS PACKAGE.
